## Arrikto Pipeline
https://codelabs.arrikto.com/codelabs/minikf-kale-katib-kfserving/index.html?index=..%2F..index#0

1. Install Kubeflow with MiniKF
1. Convert you Notebook to Kubeflow Pipelines
1. Run Kubeflow Pipelines with hyperparameter tuning 
1. Server the model from the notebook
1. Automatically version the data in the notebook and pipeline steps
